|----------------|------------------|------------------------------------|
| Tools          | 8                | 6 (base + backgroundRun + check)   |
| Execution      | Blocking only    | Blocking + virtual threads (Java 21)|
| Notification   | None             | ConcurrentLinkedQueue drained per turn |
